🟢 BIT 1: Foundations (System + Linux + Networking)
👉 Goal: Understand how systems actually work
🔹 Topics to Cover:
Linux Basics
File system, permissions, processes
Commands: top, ps, grep, netstat, df, du
Networking Fundamentals
OSI Model, TCP/IP
DNS, HTTP/HTTPS, Load Balancing
System Concepts
CPU, Memory, Disk I/O
Logs & basic troubleshooting
